This is a port of siduction-irc package  to ghostbsd.
Start a suitable IRC client to enter #ghostbsd
 ghostbsd-irc provides an easy way to choose a nickname and to enter the #ghostbsd irc channel.
 ghostbsd-irc tries to catch starting an IRC client and offers frontend
 support for various X and cli IRC clients.
:
WWW: http://www.ghostbsd.org/
